<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><div><font face="arial">We received the online portion of your application and are happy to hear of your interest in Accent on Design at NY NOW.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Accent on Design is a juried section and as such applications are reviewed by an independent selection committee. Although the selection committee has already met we are continuing to review applications on the basis of space and product needs.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">To be considered the committee requires additional information be sent <u><b>via email</b></u> to support your application. Please forward the following via email as quickly as possible:<br><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Designer/company statement - <u>please include specific details about the innovation behind the products</u>&nbsp;(i.e. materials, process, function)</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Catalog/brochure indicating the products you plan to exhibit</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Wholesale pricing</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Booth display photo (reflecting your display plans)</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>10-20 examples of your current customer base</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">It is important to keep your application materials clear and concise – giving the committee all of the information they need but in a streamlined fashion. If you have any questions please let us know.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">For submission details and ”tips on applying to a juried section” please visit:&nbsp;<a href="http://nynow.com/Exhibitors/ApplicationforExhibitSpace/TipsonapplyingtoAoDandHM.aspx​">http://nynow.com/Exhibitors/ApplicationforExhibitSpace/TipsonapplyingtoAoDandHM.aspx​</a>&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Please email your supporting materials to <a href="mailto:Andrea.Colagiovanni@nynow.com">Andrea.Colagiovanni@nynow.com</a> .</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">If you have any further questions, please feel free to contact us. Otherwise, we look forward to receiving your application shortly.</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Sincerely,&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Andrea Colagiovanni</font></div><div><font face="arial">Sales Manager</font></div><div><font face="arial">914-421-3280</font></div><div><font face="arial">Andrea.Colagiovanni</font><a></a><font face="arial"><a>@nynow.com</a></font></div></div>]]></td>
